# Next.js Frontend Rules

## Structure

Use route groups: `(gift)`, `(blog)`, `(creator)`, `(admin)/commerce|editorial|creator|platform`.  
Set `data-theme="gift"` or `data-theme="creator"` in layouts.

## Rendering

- Server Components default for read pages
- Client islands only for interactive UI
- No secrets in client bundles
- Server Actions (if used) need Zod + AuthZ equal to Nest API
- Prefer Nest `/api/v1` as system of record

## State & UI

TanStack Query for server state. No Redux unless ADR. Forms: RHF+Zod. Components: shadcn/Radix restyled to theme tokens. Icons: lucide (gift); lucide+Phosphor (creator). Toasts: Sonner.

## Motion

- **GSAP** primary for Soft Gift marketing/scroll/PDP/builder storytelling (`15-gsap-motion` rule)
- **Framer Motion** only for tiny UI presence (optional)
- Checkout/cart/admin: minimal motion, max clarity

AuthZ is never UI-only hiding.
